headline: 2 Reasons to Like RSG (and 1 Not So Much)
summary: Republic Services currently trades at $228.05 per share and has shown little upside over the past six months, posting a small loss of 4.1%. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 14.9% gain during that period.
